title: From Homeless to Hit Maker to Hilarious
itunes:title: From Homeless to Hit Maker to Hilarious
description:
TUE 5/31 - The Breakfast Club sits down with Kent Jones to talk about his journey from being homeless to making the hit song "Don't Mind" and then the jokes fly with comedians Donnell Rawlings & Deray Davis.
